post.title: Still not in LA
post.content: I didn’t make it out yesterday, and so I got rebooked on a flight this morning. Now that flight has been canceled. I guess I’ll see everyone @ PDC tomorrow. I should change my flair to “I Hope I’ll Be There Soon”.
